Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was treated as trouble occurring between Dead Apostles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No penalties for us nor for Policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you heard about my big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told Flatt and the others long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister had a lot more talent than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when I think, "What if she had met Professor?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I was able to meet everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is waiting for you and Professor to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When Svin heard that you got injured, he had such a scary look on his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary look?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe he does detest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Milady Gray all right? Milady Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to suck in Milady Gray's sweet, beautiful and slightly melancholy scent now if I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you get banned from her room, Le Chien!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Le Chien! To begin with, because you—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna make a scene, leave! Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Svin! You should know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's a book you'd be delighted to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A book that guys just love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A strategy guide for a Dating Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, I heard you were a passionate researcher of Japanese games!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, looks like things are heating up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't overlook this as a spy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you being detained by Policies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a plea bargain, so they released me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,someone real, compared to a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! All of you, get out!\NLet me heal in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If they didn't make such a ruckus, I would've been discharged a lot sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they all just eager to have you back, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Father Karabo that we both made it back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved us until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was not able to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you coming out to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The case from seven years ago will be closed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Church didn't seem to want it brought back into the limelight after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one thing I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You must surely be aware of the holes in your own deduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why he summoned a Servant, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true that Ghost Liners are precious resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand how one would go so far to summon one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's simply a matter of rarity, a Jewel-class Mystic Eyes will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be a Heroic Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there is more to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd be troubled if I died right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about being necessities for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Both myself and that Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In due time, I'll face that man once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Overturn thyself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you a question, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Trisha's pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave it behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have some sort of hypothesis about that, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were on that train on personal business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking such drastic actions, confusing the crowd with a mistaken deduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there someone you wanted to lure out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying everything was what I'd intended?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it wasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overestimating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the motive is as you've deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I did assist you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Without your assistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been able to restrain that fake Caules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In hindsight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer to your question...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is something similar to you and Miss Reines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Heartless is my elder brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us were adopted children of Norwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I have one more question to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you give up on bidding and drop out in the final phase?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If Reines took five more minutes to arrive, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you trusting Policies by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Elder brother and Gray have just been discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do people say you unfortunately miss out on things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I came here to see the two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you helped out with treatment on my elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't afford Animusphere to owe a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I do appreciate what he did about Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord El-Melloi spoke her words on her behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If this was my elder brother, he'd say,\N"Please add the suffix II."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,would not even see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Greater Grail met Father's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Marisbury's expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure his dream would've been realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is a time and a world unbeknownst to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to be such the poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you want a fair exchange of information, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We are both in line to succeed the title of Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a bad thing to use this opportunity to deepen our relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are quite different from that elder brother of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course. We're not related by blood after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I think I can be good friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to be of acquaintance as long as we can be of utility for one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Melvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a special stockholders' meeting at mom's hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a huge mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Magi do have lives, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I tune the damaged main crest of the El-Melloi faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But separate from that, I'm also in possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of Waver's magic crest for the Velvet family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic crest! The thing magi inherit from one generation to another!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What you could say is the biggest family heirloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have it, Mr. Melvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how Waver shouldered all of El-Melloi's debt from Lady Reines, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What he used as collateral for it was his magic crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone was holding it for him, I'd be the natural choice as a tuner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,took something that important to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best collateral to collect in terms of not making a magus betray you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's synonymous as taking their purpose in life away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Their purpose in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I've been curious for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you call him "Waver," Mr. Melvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it'd be lonely if nobody called him Waver
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when he relinquishes the title of Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be true that the Holy Grail War\Naffected Waver greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the 19 years leading up to that must've been valuable for him, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That, and the time after he stops being a Lord,\Nwhich will arrive at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When he is no longer a Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've never thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been changing until now, triggered by trivial things, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll continue to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, something like the Fifth Holy Grail War.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that happens, he may perhaps depart from this place for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that were to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Master will still be Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be for everyone in the class, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think that's fine in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Various people have varying sides to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun to chat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wandering child adrift in darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer with thy name establishing thee within this transient world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Svin Glascheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I seek to reach the Root using the wisdom of the beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thou art a child of the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In this moment, thou art born of darkness and given life within the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,On my name as Lord El-Melloi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I grant thee, Svin Glascheit, the rank of Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one of my students has surpassed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident in how to use my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come this far all thanks to you, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and probably Flatt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to being taught by none other than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we will conclude the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All witnesses, please greet with great applause our blessed child seeking the Root!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet another one of his students rise to the third rank of the Clock Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness gracious, your performance is a bit scary, Lord El-Melloi II.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you really are amazing, Svin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget about you, genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's not like I'm graduating or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just getting all set to fall from a child prodigy to a normal person at age 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not complimenting me at all, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not thundering down on them like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a surprisingly good mood, elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally feel like a burden has been lifted from my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm troubled if you sound like an old man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,just because you have one more student with a Pride rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As my tutor, you need to—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I must continue to get up close and intimate with who I am spying on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He may perhaps depart from this place for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, you're drinking a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, I may be a cheap drunk, but this much won't affect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, Reines was drinking ten times as much during that party earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel Miss Reines holds her drink a bit too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It will affect your performance tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The party was very lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not often that you see someone rise to Pride while in their teens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my predecessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, my predecessor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kayneth El-Melloi Archibald, was established as a child prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And pushing all other factions aside, he reigned as a great Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That was likely because everyone had to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the scenery that he'd been seeing was ideal for magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scenery that I couldn't share to the end. Not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the side of simply celebrating
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and sending out my students as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been saved thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've brought me out of that village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone appreciates you for all sorts of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Svin told me the same thing earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Perpetually a half-assed Lord incapable of doing anything like his great predecessor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think that way about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But if all of you guys tell me what you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe just a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,will you be heading out after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,About the Fifth Holy Grail War...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I officially...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,stepped down from contention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Participating in a Holy Grail War is settling matters for me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't settling matters for the Heroic Spirit Iskandar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my regrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's nothing to be so fixated over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As one of his subjects
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and as a Lord of the Clock Tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the battlefield where I need to bring things to an end is not over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dismantle the ploy he's trying to achieve by using Faker's,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words Iskandar's, power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That, in fact, is what my duty is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray, can you stand aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it at the department store with Miss Reines and company...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was thinking about giving this to you sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure accepting something like this isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not always telling you, Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The whydunit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is why you went through with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm sure my powers won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to fight together with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm counting on you in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow... It's early this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Le Chien?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that when it snows in Japan, dogs run around on the bottom right of your screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're mixing two things in that statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is new. You're not quipping with the usual "Don't call me a dog"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was told to stay calm to suit my rank of Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've matured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not just me, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Everyone has learned from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where, where? Where's Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happened to staying calm to suit your rank of Pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,one of my students...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is headed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can assault him as much as you want now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ahead and take his lips now or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You coming over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Merely an illusion that my brain and my memories have created.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? You've gotten to wringing out words in some logical manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I lecture all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think you'd be a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete with creases between your brows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Holy Grail War is over, life continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point of absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, I've changed a bit since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The one thing I can say, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I still can't stand alongside you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the pain of the path leading there and the glory at its end
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,must be gained in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but in my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the battlefield of Lord El-Melloi II!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I, as a transient dream, shall dare to ask this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Has your journey so far been fun for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow in your legacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're starting class now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:10.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
